    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>由 jonniemadeit 创建</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款超休闲且温馨的横版平台游戏，适合所有年龄段。控制一个有手臂的毛茸茸小球，穿越独特的手绘卡通世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>你能到达终点吗？！并且准时把叔叔 Unco 送到公交车站吗？</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106560/extras/2492c80dd3c5029ad9bc53b021104b92.poster.avif?t=1734185630\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106560/extras/2492c80dd3c5029ad9bc53b021104b92.webm?t=1734185630\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106560/extras/2492c80dd3c5029ad9bc53b021104b92.mp4?t=1734185630\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Uncle Unco》中的乐趣：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集所有 9 顶帽子</strong> – 找到所有帽子，定制你的球球，让它看起来更酷！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>挑战时间</strong> – 快速滚动，高高跳跃，冲向终点！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适合所有人</strong> – 充满正能量的乐趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>易学难精</strong> – 每次玩都会有新挑战！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>适合谁玩？</strong> – 儿童、休闲玩家、速通玩家和完美主义者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>内容</strong> – 适合所有玩家，尤其是喜欢挑战的直播主！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏感觉</strong> – 平滑且搞笑的操作，让游戏既独特又有趣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独立游戏社区</strong> – 加入独立游戏爱好者的社区！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>获奖</strong> – 本作荣获业内顶级专家评选的奖项。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>隐藏的宝石</strong> – 一款独立游戏圈中的隐藏宝石。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>温馨轻松</strong> – 一段短暂而激动人心的旅程，带来满满的欢乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>开发者寄语：</strong><br>在多年创作短小精悍的游戏后，我想做一款轻松的游戏，让我的侄子侄女也能玩。我希望《Uncle Unco》能带给你们和我一样的快乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >– <strong>Jonniemadeit</strong></p>",
